    "description": "This is a puzzle game using numbers. You can think carefully, because there is no time limit. Puzzles are created automatically, so each time you start a new game, a different puzzle is generated.  You can enjoy it again and again, even after you have solved all the puzzles.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE STORY</h2>The Lady Hilde ran away from home, accompanied by an impromptu retinue. And what they found was a dubious dungeon where magic was enchanted. At the entrance of the dungeon, there was a man giving a warning. However, the Lady Hilde, who knows her skills, did not listen to the warning and dived into the dungeon. What kind of ending awaits them?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>This is a puzzle game using numbers.<br></li><li>She can only move 3 squares ahead horizontally or vertically, or 2 squares ahead diagonally.<br></li><li>Monsters must be present at the destination of  her.<br></li><li>The destination monster must be weaker than her. <br></li><li>She gets stronger by one, with each monster she defeats.<br></li><li>Once all monsters have been defeated, a staircase will appear that leads further down.<br></li><li>Conquer up to 30 underground floors! </li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274730/extras/806870440b4da8d1ad261efc06fc9289.avif?t=1682496039\" width=512 height=512 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274730/extras/f5d89fb29da566c49ab50bfb17c79ede.avif?t=1682496039\" width=512 height=512 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2274730/extras/e01432059140a48dc1093b8ad6cb4e41.avif?t=1682496039\" width=512 height=512 /></span>",
